text: Mshindo Msolla is a Tanzanian professional football manager. Until 2002 he coached the club Taifa Stars.allAfrica.com: Kenya: Taifa Stars Coach Quits. May 23, 2002. From October 2002 to July 2003 he led the Tanzania national football team.\- Tanzania coach resigns - BBC News. July 22, 2003 Then he again coached the club Taifa Stars.uote of the week: 'I would only retain Mbuyu Twite'- Mshindo Msola. - Goal.com.
